cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CE 

This paper proposes a sequential optimization framework for vehicle speed trajectory planning and powertrain control in hybrid electric CAVs, which involves control systems (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational engineering (cs.CE). The focus of the paper is on the thermal responses of the engine and aftertreatment systems, which are related to the control and optimization of the powertrain.
